# Cursor codebase indexing exclusions for dr-claw
# ------------------------------------------------
# Files matched here are skipped by Cursor's semantic codebase index, but the
# agent (and you) can still open and read them on demand. This is the right
# choice for low-signal or binary-heavy files.
#
# Note: Cursor's indexer already honors .gitignore, so node_modules/, dist/,
# release/, .runtime/, coverage/ etc. are excluded automatically — no need to
# repeat them here.

# --- Lockfiles (large, no semantic value) ---
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
pnpm-lock.yaml

# --- Auto-generated docs ---
CHANGELOG.md

# --- Source maps & minified bundles ---
**/*.map
**/*.min.js
**/*.min.css

# --- Binary assets (images, icons, fonts) ---
**/*.png
**/*.jpg
**/*.jpeg
**/*.gif
**/*.ico
**/*.icns
**/*.webp
**/*.bmp
**/*.tiff
**/*.svg
**/*.woff
**/*.woff2
**/*.ttf
**/*.otf
**/*.eot
**/*.mp4
**/*.mov
**/*.webm
**/*.mp3
**/*.wav
**/*.pdf

# --- Native modules / compiled artifacts ---
**/*.node
**/*.dylib
**/*.so
**/*.dll
**/build/Release/

# --- Generated PWA artifacts ---
public/sw.js
public/manifest.json

# --- Static HTML in public/ (not application source) ---
public/api-docs.html
public/clear-cache.html

# --- Database snapshots / dumps (also covered by .gitignore but explicit) ---
**/*.db
**/*.sqlite
**/*.sqlite3

# --- Archive files ---
**/*.zip
**/*.tar
**/*.tar.gz
**/*.tgz
**/*.7z
